{"tid":2000072,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［搵Game］想搵返細個玩過隻DOS game","createTime":"2020-05-03T15:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T16:56:06.000Z","uid":98761,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bdfdda2a36d1346c0eee637fcea2e1c6b3aef9aa","tid":2000072,"uid":98761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"細個果時有個同學成日拎隻Dos game上黎屋企玩<br />\n一路都打唔爆<br />\n而家想搵返佢出黎打爆佢 但又唔知隻game叫咩名...<br />\n資訊唔多，希望有清記得隻game<br />\n隻game係橫向過版game<br />\n主角好似係一個鍊金師定魔術師咁既人<br />\n其中有一招係掟個硬幣出去 就可以移型換影<br />\n<br />\n有無辦法搵得返隻game黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873da928099dcf371a67e2931eb2301ca1b9a66a","tid":2000072,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"依度有大量DOS game<br />\n<a href=\"https://archive.org/details/softwarelibrary_msdos_games\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fsoftwarelibrary_msdos_games&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=29e3c96f\" target=\"_blank\">https://archive.org/details/softwarelibrary_msdos_games</a>"},{"pid":"313a6cbddd9cd0b1c097af4d9db0ebce29c5dce8","tid":2000072,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:19:53.000Z","msg":"我有記憶既係 <br />\n猩猩擲蕉<br />\n高報酬戰將<br />\n仲有隻農場"},{"pid":"32074de89eb1cff08ff15b4fca6d6d8465101044","tid":2000072,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:21:36.000Z","msg":"Dune 2<br />\nC and c<br />\nSim city"},{"pid":"e34a62ab5723b1d6e02eb2837c6392ce51b6b7c1","tid":2000072,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"有個網叫骨灰集散地<br />\nhkgeocities年代"},{"pid":"623025f129d24aec3d39892e8368eb97e7c9f3f5","tid":2000072,"uid":98761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"873da928099dcf371a67e2931eb2301ca1b9a66a","tid"